  "description": "A PocketMine-MP plugin that disallows players from joining your server through VPNs.",
  "readme_markdown": "<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-novpn\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#novpn\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>NoVPN</h1>\n<p>A PocketMine-MP plugin that disallows players from joining your server through VPNs.<br>\n<strong>NOTE:</strong> You will need to create an account on <a href=\"https://antivpn.cosmicpe.me/client\" rel=\"nofollow\">CosmicPE Anti-VPN</a> and paste your API key in <code>config.yml</code> (<a href=\"https://github.com/Cosmoverse/NoVPN/blob/master/resources/config.yml#L4\">in the <code>api-key</code> field</a>) before using this plugin.</p>\n<script defer src=\"https://static.cloudflareinsights.com/beacon.min.js/v8c78df7c7c0f484497ecbca7046644da1771523124516\" integrity=\"sha512-8DS7rgIrAmghBFwoOTujcf6D9rXvH8xm8JQ1Ja01h9QX8EzXldiszufYa4IFfKdLUKTTrnSFXLDkUEOTrZQ8Qg==\" data-cf-beacon='{\"version\":\"2024.11.0\",\"token\":\"508eb1d242ef46b690a0886422106e77\",\"r\":1,\"server_timing\":{\"name\":{\"cfCacheStatus\":true,\"cfEdge\":true,\"cfExtPri\":true,\"cfL4\":true,\"cfOrigin\":true,\"cfSpeedBrain\":true},\"location_startswith\":null}}' crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>",
